# 安装Kernel
# poetry run python -m ipykernel install --user --name quant-portfolio

import sys
sys.path.append('..')

from portfolio_analysis.data_loader import load_data
from portfolio_analysis.optimizer import optimize_portfolio
from portfolio_analysis.backtester import backtest
from portfolio_analysis.visualizer import plot_cumulative_returns
import holoviews as hv
hv.extension('bokeh')

# 加载数据
returns = load_data(['AAPL', 'MSFT', 'GOOG', 'AMZN'], '2020-01-01', '2024-01-01')

# 优化组合
portfolio = optimize_portfolio(returns)

# 回测
cumulative_returns = backtest(portfolio, returns)

# 可视化
plot_cumulative_returns(cumulative_returns)
